        void startGUIRefresh(int refreshRateInMilliSeconds)
        Starts the GUI refresh function. Time in milli seconds. Times smaller 100 ms are not provided. NOTICE!!!!!!!!!!!!! supported values: UpDown: Range [0-100]; LeftRight: Range [0-100]; BackForth: Range [0-100]; OpenClose: Range [0-100];
